dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.bswmoduletemplate.bswbehavior

Interface IBswEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAbstractEvent, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBswAsynchronousServerCallReturnsEvent, IBswBackgroundEvent, IBswDataReceivedEvent, IBswExternalTriggerOccurredEvent, IBswInternalTriggerOccurredEvent, IBswModeManagerErrorEvent, IBswModeSwitchedAckEvent, IBswModeSwitchEvent, IBswOperationInvokedEvent, IBswScheduleEvent, IBswTimingEvent

    public interface IBswEvent
extends IEntity, IAbstractEvent
    IBswEvent: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Base class of various kinds of events which are used to trigger a BswModuleEntity of this BSW module or cluster. The event is local to the BSW module or cluster. The short name of the meta-class instance is intended as an input to configure the required API of the BSW Scheduler.
